"children\":\"100% Free, No Catch\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"No subscriptions, no freemium limits, no \\\"free trial\\\" that expires in 7 days. Our tools are ad-supported so they stay free for everyone.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 text-brand\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\",\"key\":\"oel41y\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-shield size-5\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Private by Design\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Everything runs in your browser. Your files, data, and documents never leave your device — we can't see them, and neither can anyone else.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 text-brand\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\",\"key\":\"1xq2db\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-zap size-5\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold\",\"children\":\"No Sign Up Required\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Just open a tool and start using it. No account creation, no email verification, no onboarding flow. Your time matters.\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"How It Works\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Every tool on Free Tool Shed is a standalone web application that runs entirely in your browser. When you create an invoice, build a resume, or use any of our tools, the processing happens on your machine using modern web technologies like WebAssembly and the Web Audio API. There are no servers storing your data and no cloud accounts to manage.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Your work is automatically saved to your browser's local storage so you can pick up where you left off. When you're ready, export your finished work as a PDF or other standard format — the file goes straight to your device.\"}]]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"More Tools on the Way\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[\"We're actively building new tools and adding them regularly. From document editors and image converters to calculators and data formatters — if there's a paid tool that should be free, we're working on it. Bookmark this page and check back soon, or\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"text-brand underline underline-offset-4\",\"children\":\"let us know\"}],\" \",\"which tool you'd like to see next.\"]}]]}]\n23:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/064cw2la3d-ye.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n24:[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$28\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@2c\"}]}]\n26:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n2d:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chun